er": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 35, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8503882, "raw_content": "I think that we have to admit what is going to happen now.\nI'm not trying to be a blackpill, but gas is approaching 4-5 dollars a gallon.\nWe are in a war that won't be over in the forseeable future.\nThe market is crashing.\n\n\nTrump was forced into this war by Israel and now the GOP is going to pay the price.\n\nI know this will be downvoted, I know I could risk a ban.\n\nBut I think we need to face the facts here.\n\nThere are people I know who were hardcore Maga who don't even care anymore, they likely won't even vote in the midterms.\n\nThis war was the nail in the coffin.\n\nEDIT:\n\nI have noticed no one in the comments have given me a counter point as to why this isn't the case. I will be waiting.", "author": "new_guy3", "created": 1774107745120, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "ShinAkuma", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Trump handed the left the midterms", "last_comment_created": 1774119654262, "content": "<p>I think that we have to admit what is going to happen now.\nI'm not trying to be a blackpill, but gas is approaching 4-5 dollars a gallon.\nWe are in a war that won't be over in the forseeable future.\nThe market is crashing.</p>\n<p>Trump was forced into this war by Israel and now the GOP is going to pay the price.</p>\n<p>I know this will be downvoted, I know I could risk a ban.</p>\n<p>But I think we need to face the facts here.</p>\n<p>There are people I know who were hardcore Maga who don't even care anymore, they likely won't even vote in the midterms.</p>\n<p>This war was the nail in the coffin.</p>\n<p>EDIT:</p>\n<p>I have noticed no one in the comments have given me a counter point as to why this isn't the case. I will be waiting.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 2, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 38, "score_up": 35, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 1, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASYyw8aHY", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 22, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8504170, "raw_content": "Figured he was a pedophile just because democrats liked him. Not talking about that aspect. He never should have been \u201chonored\u201d in any way to begin with. Democrats are now at light speed removing him from everything and pretending they never supported this. This is not done out of moral outrage over what he did. This is done because they got caught and it makes them look bad. Nobody will be held accountable for putting up statues of a pedophile. These actions are the coverup of what he did and who supported him in doing it. Not accountability for him or the people who helped him in any way. And the GOP, like always, are just letting them cover it up with zero pushback. Where\u2019s the Chavez list? Why don\u2019t we have a list of everyone who funded him, supported him, met with him, and gave him access to children? He was a rapist. So where is all that? No, we just get the coverup done quietly and democrats will claim they never ever supported him a year or two from now. ", "author": "lefty295", "created": 1774116720156, "profile_picture": "NWbNd6AomP4v", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Cali_kid", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "This Chavez stuff is dystopian. This is not an endorsement of him in any way. But we are seeing a coverup. Not accountability with this.", "last_comment_created": 1774117316221, "content": "<p>Figured he was a pedophile just because democrats liked him. Not talking about that aspect. He never should have been \u201chonored\u201d in any way to begin with. Democrats are now at light speed removing him from everything and pretending they never supported this. This is not done out of moral outrage over what he did. This is done because they got caught and it makes them look bad. Nobody will be held accountable for putting up statues of a pedophile. These actions are the coverup of what he did and who supported him in doing it. Not accountability for him or the people who helped him in any way. And the GOP, like always, are just letting them cover it up with zero pushback. Where\u2019s the Chavez list? Why don\u2019t we have a list of everyone who funded him, supported him, met with him, and gave him access to children? He was a rapist. So where is all that? No, we just get the coverup done quietly and democrats will claim they never ever supported him a year or two from now.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 22, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2035047471378817258", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASYyv2Np1", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 32, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8503927, "raw_content": "", "author": "SALTYinSeattle", "created": 1774109339482, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald